    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>When you use a junkbot grenade, you set it to either handy or healing, then throw it into a pile of inert technological equipment of at least 1 bulk. When the grenade lands, it spreads magical nanites over the blast radius. Over the course of the next round, the nanites convert the junk into a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.TQV8YIT3HlhSszMr]{Handy Junkbot} or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.J9H196LxSVvMguhe]{Healing Junkbot}, as those spells except as detailed here. Either spell has a caster level of 9th. You must command the junkbot verbally. The junkbot created from this effect lasts for 1 minute.</p>"
